Class ReportCriteria

java.lang.Object
src.report.ReportCriteria
public class ReportCriteria extends Object
Encapsulates criteria for filtering and sorting internship reports.

Allows specifying optional filters for title, major, level, company, status, dates, visibility, and minimum slots. Also supports specifying a sort order for results.
